Feature: Compare Plans on Quote Side-By-Side
  As a User
  I want to be able to compare my plans side by side
  So that I can make the best plan selection decisions for my client and their employees

  Scenario: Carrier logos should display for each carrier plan

  Scenario: Marketplace logos should display for each marketplace plan

  Scenario: Set of benefits display for each plan on a quote

  Scenario: 4-Tier and 3-Tier plans should show rate breakdowns for each plan

  Scenario: Number of members assigned to a plan display for each plan on a quote

  Scenario: Current coverage plans display on a quote

  Scenario: Both current and renewal coverage plans display on a quote

  Scenario: Change side-by-side position of a plan on quote

  Scenario: Move plan 1 position left/right on a side-by-side view

  Scenario: Sort plans on side-by-side view of a quote

  Scenario: Filter plans on side-by-side view of a quote by state

  Scenario: Filter plans on side-by-side view of a quote by ZIP code
